nuary   the aeo brand operated  stores and online at wwwaecomaeriethe companys aerie is an intimates brand it offers bras undies swim sleep and apparel among others as of january   the aerie brand operated  standalone stores and  sidebyside stores connected to aeo brand stores in addition the aerie brand merchandise is sold online at wwwaeriecom and certain items are sold in aeo brand storesother brandsthe companys other brands include tailgate and todd snyder new york tailgate is an apparel brand with a college town store concept as of january   the tailgate brand operated four stores and was available online at wwwaecom todd snyder new york is a menswear brand as of january   the todd snyder brand operated one store and online at wwwtoddsnydercom » full overview of aeo company address american eagle outfitters inc  hot metal stpittsburgh   pa    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation jay schottenstein  robert madore  jennifer foyle  charles kessler  michael rempell  » more officers  directors american eagle outfitters inc news american eagle forecasts dismal secondquarter amid stiff competition may   update american eagle forecasts dismal q amid stiff competition may   american eagle posts surprise rise in comparable sales may   briefamerican eagle outfitters declares regular quarterly dividend of  per share mar   briefamerican eagle outfitters reports q earnings per share  mar   » more aeo news related topics stocksstock screenerapparel  accessories retailers american eagle outfitters inc  company profile from hoover’s  db hoovers menu buy reports  lists how it works united states united kingdom   login company people industry search db hoovers company  people  industry login avention onesource is now db hoovers login here for access to db hoovers db datavision db business browser and isell login for customers of hoovers prior to march   login call   chat software by boldchat start free trial call   chat software by boldchat start 