verage a simple moving average sma is an arithmetic moving average calculated by adding the closing price of the security for a number of time periods and then dividing this total by the number of time periods a simple moving average smoothes out volatility and makes it easier to view the price trend of a security if the simple moving average points up this means that the security’s price is increasing if it is pointing down it means that the security’s price is decreasing the longer the timeframe for the moving average the smoother the simple moving average a shorterterm moving average is more volatile but its reading is closer to the source data  related articlesmore from authorjb hunt transport services inc jbht registers a price change of  while sonic corp sonc finishes with a flow of air lease corporation al is at  per share and manpowergroup inc man is listed at blue apron holdings inc aprn is at  per share and westinghouse air brake technologies corporation wab is listed at leave a reply cancel replyplease enter your comment please enter your name here you have entered an incorrect email addressplease enter your email address here latest newsdepomed inc depo noted a price change of  and protalix ross arlen  july  omeros corporation omer has a value of  per share while ross arlen  july  acadia healthcare company inc achc noted a price change of  ross arlen  july   technology updatesred hat inc rht noted a price change of  and july  a networks inc aten noted a price change of  and july  amphenol corporation aph has a value of  per share while july  intuit inc intu has a value of  per share while july  microsemi corporation mscc has a value of  per share while july  healthcare updatesdepomed inc depo noted a price change of  and protalix july  rigel pharmaceuticals inc rigl noted a price change of  and july  quest diagnostics incorporated dgx noted a price change of  and july  halozyme therapeutics inc halo has a value of  per share july  lexicon pharmaceuticals